THE 24-year-old mum who allegedly killed four of her
children has abandoned her bail application at the Emalahleni Magistrate's
Court. Zinhle Maditla, however applied for mental observation. Zinhle Maditla from Klarinet, Mpumalanga, missed her first
appearance at the Witbank Magistrates Court on 2 January as she was in
hospital. Maditlaâ€™s children, aged between 11 months and eight years
of age, were last seen on 26 December. Their bodies, which were wrapped in blankets, were found
